{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/aws/230119_ec2_start/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"MHLab blog","author":"MHLab"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6515c56d-354f-5b3d-9900-52fe0630e21d","excerpt":"이제 새롭게 시작할 서비스를 구성하며... 난 주로 EC2의 무료 플랜을 1년 굴려보고 희망이 보이면 그땐 제대로 하고, 그 외는 개발용으로 두고 종료한다. 이번에도 서비스를 올리려고 또 아마존에서 EC2 작업을 하다가 기록을 남긴다.\n먼저 AWS…","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 638px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8ab6e7f2f9c288cc06ffe863977e3320/8608d/thumbnail.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.44171779141104%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"thumbnail\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8ab6e7f2f9c288cc06ffe863977e3320/8608d/thumbnail.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8ab6e7f2f9c288cc06ffe863977e3320/d2f63/thumbnail.jpg 163w,\n/static/8ab6e7f2f9c288cc06ffe863977e3320/c989d/thumbnail.jpg 325w,\n/static/8ab6e7f2f9c288cc06ffe863977e3320/8608d/thumbnail.jpg 638w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 638px) 100vw, 638px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"이제-새롭게-시작할-서비스를-구성하며\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%9C-%EC%83%88%EB%A1%AD%EA%B2%8C-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%A0-%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0\" aria-label=\"이제 새롭게 시작할 서비스를 구성하며 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이제 새롭게 시작할 서비스를 구성하며...</h1>\n<p>난 주로 EC2의 무료 플랜을 1년 굴려보고 희망이 보이면 그땐 제대로 하고,<br>\n그 외는 개발용으로 두고 종료한다.</p>\n<p>이번에도 서비스를 올리려고 또 아마존에서 EC2 작업을 하다가 기록을 남긴다.\n먼저 AWS에 가입이 되어 있고, 계정이 다 있다는 가정하에 진행한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"먼저-ec2-선택부터\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A8%BC%EC%A0%80-ec2-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EB%B6%80%ED%84%B0\" aria-label=\"먼저 ec2 선택부터 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>먼저 EC2 선택부터</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/e35ec/img01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 126.99386503067484%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/a6d36/img01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/222b7/img01.png 163w,\n/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/ff46a/img01.png 325w,\n/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/a6d36/img01.png 650w,\n/static/615f1b5af3c39c60987bdc6703e22b8d/e35ec/img01.png 861w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>난 Ubuntu가 편하여 LTS 버전으로 선택해줬다.<br>\n본인이 원하는 OS가 있다면 그것으로 해도 무방하다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/cda19/img02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 136.80981595092027%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/a6d36/img02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/222b7/img02.png 163w,\n/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/ff46a/img02.png 325w,\n/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/a6d36/img02.png 650w,\n/static/307d82ffc6d2bdfe152ce772b9bbac00/cda19/img02.png 785w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그 다음은 인스턴스는 일단 프리티어에 맞는걸로 해준다.<br>\n서비스가 잘 되서 확장하는게 아닌 이상 일단 맛보기용으로 운영하기에도 스팩이 나쁘지 않다.</p>\n<p>키페어는 이 인스턴스에 접근할 때 쓸 공개/비밀 키를 생성하는 부분인데,<br>\n난 키 하나로 돌려 쓰는게 아니라 하나의 인스턴스 당 하나의 키를 소유하게끔 한다. (너무 당연한 이야기...-_-;;)</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/321ea/img03.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.52760736196319%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img03\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/a6d36/img03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/222b7/img03.png 163w,\n/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/ff46a/img03.png 325w,\n/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/a6d36/img03.png 650w,\n/static/52a857dc0a75fd7c7d535230aba64e0f/321ea/img03.png 786w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>보안그룹은 가급적 제한된 IP만 제공하는게 좋다.<br>\n나는 일단 ssh만 열어뒀다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/96e92/img04.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.62576687116564%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img04\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/a6d36/img04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/222b7/img04.png 163w,\n/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/ff46a/img04.png 325w,\n/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/a6d36/img04.png 650w,\n/static/39eef9e401ea33ad1841fc319a4d11b6/96e92/img04.png 779w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>스토리지는 10기가로 되어 있는데, 프리티어는 30기가까지 가능하기에 30을 맞춰준다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/b94e3/img05.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.012269938650306%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img05\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/a6d36/img05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/222b7/img05.png 163w,\n/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/ff46a/img05.png 325w,\n/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/a6d36/img05.png 650w,\n/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/e548f/img05.png 975w,\n/static/aee7c65e43899b7fb2c7aad1ba6862e8/b94e3/img05.png 1126w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그 다음 큰 특이사항이 없다면 생성해준다.<br>\n그리고 혹시 모르니 결제 알림은 생성해준다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/716847cabbf1453cb410ce8c1b577f73/a13c9/img06.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.49079754601227%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img06\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/716847cabbf1453cb410ce8c1b577f73/a6d36/img06.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/716847cabbf1453cb410ce8c1b577f73/222b7/img06.png 163w,\n/static/716847cabbf1453cb410ce8c1b577f73/ff46a/img06.png 325w,\n/static/716847cabbf1453cb410ce8c1b577f73/a6d36/img06.png 650w,\n/static/716847cabbf1453cb410ce8c1b577f73/e548f/img06.png 975w,\n/static/716847cabbf1453cb410ce8c1b577f73/a13c9/img06.png 1178w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>그리고 EC2 내역으로 와서 조금만 기다리면 인스턴스가 준비된다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/6fcb6/img07.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 11.042944785276074%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAcUlEQVR42iWN6w0DMQiDb//J2hFOHSEJIQHyVEo5+uOTjcHiCjFqIVHmP3NOHcNwHdp792yvrWst94/uvd1P88t25xzPLxbplegmogCQ362NT8KkGbMmAC21KhTQXA1En0OI3+dRQgTrvEQk2O3NzO0H5YqZSKQ1II4AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img07\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/a6d36/img07.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/222b7/img07.png 163w,\n/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/ff46a/img07.png 325w,\n/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/a6d36/img07.png 650w,\n/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/e548f/img07.png 975w,\n/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/3c492/img07.png 1300w,\n/static/b65d5b8d0085c2a618fb347b8d35555d/6fcb6/img07.png 1523w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>이것을 연결하기 위해서는 연결 항목을 참고하면 되는데 아래와 같이 가이드 되어 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f5c897a655157c55e6460f3797fa91a6/bcb8c/img09.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 73.00613496932516%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img09\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f5c897a655157c55e6460f3797fa91a6/a6d36/img09.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f5c897a655157c55e6460f3797fa91a6/222b7/img09.png 163w,\n/static/f5c897a655157c55e6460f3797fa91a6/ff46a/img09.png 325w,\n/static/f5c897a655157c55e6460f3797fa91a6/a6d36/img09.png 650w,\n/static/f5c897a655157c55e6460f3797fa91a6/bcb8c/img09.png 879w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>개인정보가 많아서 좀 많이 지워졌다 -_-;;<br>\n자세한 것은 아래에서 다루겠다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"local에서-접근하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#local%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"local에서 접근하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Local에서 접근하기</h2>\n<p>아까 받은 pem 파일을 적당한 곳에 배치하고, 해당 파일의 권한을 바꿔줘야 한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ chmod 400 ./my_key.pem</code></pre></div>\n<p>만약 권한을 조정하지 않고 사용할 경우 아래와 같은 에러를 받을 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ab21ade9d4f7fb51d87d8011ac8c0c72/99072/img10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.926380368098158%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img10\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/ab21ade9d4f7fb51d87d8011ac8c0c72/a6d36/img10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ab21ade9d4f7fb51d87d8011ac8c0c72/222b7/img10.png 163w,\n/static/ab21ade9d4f7fb51d87d8011ac8c0c72/ff46a/img10.png 325w,\n/static/ab21ade9d4f7fb51d87d8011ac8c0c72/a6d36/img10.png 650w,\n/static/ab21ade9d4f7fb51d87d8011ac8c0c72/99072/img10.png 842w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>권한 조정을 하고 아래 명령어를 통해서 접속할 수 있다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\"># ssh -i [key 파일 경로와 파일명] [아까 aws에서 받은 계정명과 주소(이 부분은 연결 정보에서 확인 가능하다.)]\n\n$ ssh -i \"./my_key.pem\" user@.compute.amazonaws.com</code></pre></div>\n<p>난 이걸 shell로 짜서 그냥 한번에 접근하게 해둔다.<br>\n별건 아니고 위의 명령어를 <strong>xxx.sh</strong>로 만들어서</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>./my_aws.sh</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>이런식으로?</p>\n<br>\n<h3 id=\"정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"정리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정리</h3>\n<p>영양가 없는 포스팅이었지만...<br>\n또 잊을까봐 나를 위해서 정리한 포스팅으로 만족해야겠다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"toc\"><pre class=\"language-toc\"><code class=\"language-toc\"></code></pre></div>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%9C-%EC%83%88%EB%A1%AD%EA%B2%8C-%EC%8B%9C%EC%9E%91%ED%95%A0-%EC%84%9C%EB%B9%84%EC%8A%A4%EB%A5%BC-%EA%B5%AC%EC%84%B1%ED%95%98%EB%A9%B0\">이제 새롭게 시작할 서비스를 구성하며...</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%A8%BC%EC%A0%80-ec2-%EC%84%A0%ED%83%9D%EB%B6%80%ED%84%B0\">먼저 EC2 선택부터</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#local%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">Local에서 접근하기</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\">정리</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"AWS EC2 프리티어 시작하기","description":"Aws EC2 프리티어","date":"January 19, 2023","tags":["Aws","Ubuntu","EC2","Infra"],"series":"Aws","previewImage":"aws_logo.webp","isPrivate":null,"writer":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/vcs_git/230118_git_ssh_key/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Github clone 받을 때 권한 문제 (git permission denied - publickey)","isPrivate":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/aws/230119_buy_domain/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Aws에서 도메인 구입 후 연결하기 (With 흑우집합소)","isPrivate":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"6515c56d-354f-5b3d-9900-52fe0630e21d","previousPostId":"ecbb5ac5-bccd-532a-ad2d-04a11aca70a0","nextPostId":"36b28373-8033-5dce-9944-fc7af873e270"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}